    <div class="forum-post-panel-main clear-block">
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi,</p>

<p>I run v0.9.12, under linux (ubuntu, archlinux and mandriva).</p>

<p>When I run the server for a LAN, every client can connect. they see each other, they can chat.</p>

<p>But in the chat room no room name is diplayed, even if a player has created one. </p>

<p>So it's impossible to play together, as nobody can join others player's room.</p>

<p>Is this a known issue ?</p>      </div>

          </div>
