      <div class="content">
        <p>That's it ! I didn't notice that ubuntu and mandriva's packages were shipping v0.9.11. I tested and as I use the hedgewars server in ubuntu, there are no issues when two client with v0.9.11 are connected.</p>

<p>Thanks !</p>      </div>

